<div style='display: inline; float: right;'><image itemprop='image' class='filephoto' alt='USS Langley (CVL-27) file photo [15296]' title='USS Langley (CVL-27) file photo [15296]' src='/images/ship_langleyindependence1.jpg' /><script>
